text: Kim Nam-soon (born May 7, 1980) is a South Korean archer. She won both a gold and a silver medal at the 2000 Summer Olympics.Olympic resultsKim Nam-Sun == References == Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:Archers Category:Olympic gold medalists for South Korea Category:Olympic silver medalists for South Korea Category:Medalists at the 2000 Summer Olympics
